skeleton.config_file:
# Cargo configuration for optimized builds and custom output directories

[build]
# Platform-specific linker optimization
[target.'cfg(windows)']
rustflags = [
    "-C", "link-arg=/SUBSYSTEM:CONSOLE",
    "-C", "link-arg=/OPT:REF,ICF",
    "-C", "target-cpu=native",
    "-C", "codegen-units=1"
]

[target.'cfg(unix)']
rustflags = [
    "-C", "link-arg=-Wl,--gc-sections",
    "-C", "link-arg=-Wl,--strip-all",
    "-C", "target-cpu=native",
    "-C", "codegen-units=1"
]

# Use mold linker on Linux if available (much faster than lld)
[target.'cfg(all(target_os = "linux", target_env = "gnu"))']
linker = "clang"
rustflags = [
    "-C", "link-arg=-fuse-ld=mold",
    "-C", "link-arg=-Wl,--gc-sections",
    "-C", "link-arg=-Wl,--strip-all",
    "-C", "target-cpu=native"
]

# Use lld on macOS for faster linking
[target.'cfg(target_os = "macos")']
rustflags = [
    "-C", "link-arg=-fuse-ld=lld",
    "-C", "link-arg=-Wl,-dead_strip",
    "-C", "target-cpu=native"
]

# Parallel jobs optimized for modern CPUs
#jobs = 12

[profile.release]
# Optimized for speed with reasonable binary size
opt-level = 3
lto = "thin"  # Thin LTO for faster compilation
codegen-units = 1  # Max optimization
strip = true  # Strip symbols
panic = "abort"  # Smaller panic handling
overflow-checks = false  # Disable for performance
debug = false  # No debug info

[profile.release-optimized]
# Maximum optimization for production
inherits = "release"
lto = "fat"  # Full LTO for maximum optimization
codegen-units = 1  # Single codegen unit
opt-level = 3
panic = "abort"
strip = true
overflow-checks = false
debug = false

[profile.dev]
# Fast debug builds
opt-level = 0  # No optimization for faster compilation
debug = true  # Full debug info
split-debuginfo = "unpacked"  # Faster linking
overflow-checks = true
incremental = true

[profile.test]
# Optimized test builds
inherits = "dev"
opt-level = 1  # Light optimization for tests
debug = true
incremental = true

[registries.crates-io]
protocol = "sparse"

# Cache configuration for faster builds
[env]
CARGO_TARGET_DIR = "target"
CARGO_INCREMENTAL = "1"

# Disable incremental compilation for release builds
#[target.'cfg(not(debug_assertions))']
#incremental = false
